folder: Wyckoff Ave. & Weirfield St., Brooklyn, NY
text:
Wyckoff Ave., at the S.W. corner of Weirfield Street, showing the Laibach and Ehnis' Brewery in a set of three views. It still stands in 1929. The trolley tracks are on Wyckoff Ave.

1922.

View 3:-April 1923.
